<HEADLINE> Niyongabo Withdraws from World Athletics </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, July 30 (Xinhuar) -- Olympic 5,000 meters champion
Venuste Niyongabo of Burundi has withdrawn from the Sixth World
Athletics Championships starting on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
A spokesman for the International Amateur Athletic
Federation said Niyongabo had been struggling recently with a
leg injury. 
</P>
