Moussa today that the Mideast peace talks should continue.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. diplomat made the statement a day after two bombs tore
through a crowded fruit and vegetable market in west Jerusalem
killing at least 15 people and wounding over 170 others.
</P>
<P>
