Indore city, 806 km south of New Delhi, capital of India, when the
mishap occurred.
</P>
<P>
ALGIERS -- A car bomb exploded in the Algerian capital of
Algiers Wednesday night, killing four people and injuring 25
others, Algiers Radio quoted the Security Administration of
Algeria as saying Thursday morning.
</P>
<P>
