<HEADLINE> Airport Links East China Archipelago With Mainland </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANGZHOU, July 31 (Xinhua) -- Zhujiajian Airport, based on the
Zhoushan Island, the main body of the Zhoushan Archipelago in
