<DATE_TIME> 1997-07-31 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Beijing Rally For PLA Anniversary (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A streamer hung opposite the rostrum reading "Rally closely
around the CPC Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the
core and strive to build a powerful, modernized, regular
revolutionary army."
</P>
<P>
Also present were revolutionary veterans, who made a great
contribution to the founding of new China, representatives from
various circles, and army, naval, and air force officers and men.
</P>
<P>
Delivering an important speech amid warm applause, Jiang told
of the PLA's history since its founding 70 years ago and the
army's great contribution in the Chinese revolution and the
undertakings after the founding of the new China in 1949.
</P>
<P>
He said the army's glorious 70-year history shows that the PLA
is loyal to the party and the people, that it braves all
difficulties and can defeat all enemy troops, that it has lofty
ideals, moral integrity, good education, and a strong sense of
discipline.
</P>
<P>
Jiang pointed out that the glorious history of the PLA is
inseparable from the great names of comrade Mao Zedong and comrade
Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
Comrade Mao Zedong, who was one of the main founders of the
PLA, put forward a set of principles for building the new type of
people's army during the course of the Chinese revolutionary
struggle, he said.
</P>
<P>
After the founding of the new China, he put forward the guiding
principles of building national defense and modernizing national
defense. Mao's military thought is an important part of Mao
Zedong thought, which is a creative development of the military
theory of Marxism by the Chinese Communist Party.
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping's thoughts on army building during the new period
were an inheritance and development of Mao Zedong's military
thought, and an important part of the theory of building socialism
with Chinese characteristics and a long-term guiding principle for
our army's modernization drive.
</P>
<P>
Jiang emphasized that building the army and national defense
are the common task of the party and the Chinese people of
all nationalities and that it is a fine tradition to build the
army and the national defense by relying on people.
</P>
<P>
Jiang called finally on the party, the army, and all people
across the country to unite closely together under the guidance of
the Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics and the party's basic line, working hard to build
the army into a powerful, modernized, and regular revolutionary
army, and the country into a prosperous, democratic, civilized,
and modernized socialist country. 
</P>
</TEXT>
