<HEADLINE> Peru's Trade Deficit Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LIMA, July 30 (Xinhua) -- Peru had a trade deficit equivalent
to 491 million U.S. dollars in the first half of this year, or 45
percent less than the same period last year.
</P>
