after five years of monthly deficits.
</P>
<P>
The downward trend of deficit is due to a better balance
between exports and imports. The increase in non-traditional
exports stand out among its overseas sales.
</P>
<P>
PROMPEX General Manager Antonio Castillo said the increase in
non-traditional exports was due to lower tariffs and the
elimination of trade barriers. 
