<HEADLINE> SADC to Use Satellite for land-mine Clearance </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, July 30 (Xinhua) -- The Southern African
Development Community (SADC) will introduce satellite mapping
technology to clear land mines throughout the sub-region.
</P>
<P>
